 9. the person who's sport is tennis is on the far left##1
10. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is cricket##1
11. the engineer is on the left of the paramedic##1
12. the person who's birthday is in march is on the far left##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in march##3

