 4. the owner of the goldfish is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
 5. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is soccer##3
 6. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the project-manager is the person watching spy movies##1
 8. the person watching animation movies is the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person driving the tram is in an even position##4
10. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
11. the indonesian is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
12. the person who's sport is soccer is the pilot##1
13. the german is the owner of the turtle##1

