 7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the tower house is on the left or right of the person playing mah-jongg##3
 9. the security-guard is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4
11. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the tower house##1

