.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-4-16::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, chess, magic-tricks
The people have 3 different jobs:  designer, mechanic, police-officer
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: folk, gospel, jazz
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, bongani, oliveros
3 different pets are kept: dog, guinea-pig, lizard
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, rose
The people use 3 different means of transport: bike, ship, train
 1. the person who growsazalea is on the far left##1
 2. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1
 3. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
 4. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the police-officer##1
 6. the fan of jazz is the person who growsrose##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is on the far left##1
 9. the person driving the train is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the chaman-smoker##1
11. the designer is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
12. the person who's hobby is chess is between the fan of gospel and the mechanic##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2      |       3       |
