There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, russian
3 different pets are kept: bird, cat, hamster
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, monopoly
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bike, van
 1. the argentine is in an odd position##4
 2. the owner of the bird is in an even position##4
 3. the person playing bridge is on the left or right of the person playing poker##3
 4. the person drinking iced-tea is between the person playing monopoly and the person drinking fanta##2
 5. the argentine is on the left of the person who growsrose##1
 6. the person playing monopoly is on the far left##1
 7. the person playing bridge is between the canadian and the person driving the van##2
 8. the fan of techno is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 9. the person playing poker is in an odd position##4
10. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the owner of the bird##3
11. the fan of jazz is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
12. the owner of the hamster is the person who growsiris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | milk       | iced-tea      | fanta    |
| Flower          | daisy | rose     | iris    |
| Music-Genre   | country    | techno        | jazz     |
| Nationality   | argentine  | russian       | canadian |
| Pet           | cat        | bird          | hamster  |
